{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 28", "sort_key": "0028", "text_original": "孔子曰：「婿使人吊。如婿之父母死，則女之家亦使人吊。父喪稱父，母喪稱母。父母不在，則稱伯父世母。婿，已葬，婿之伯父致命女氏曰：『某之子有父母之喪，不得嗣為兄弟，使某致命。』女氏許諾，而弗敢嫁，禮也。婿，免喪，女之父母使人請，婿弗取，而後嫁之，禮也。女之父母死，婿亦如之。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「婿使人吊。如婿之父母死，則女之家亦使人吊。父喪稱父，母喪稱母。父母不在，則稱伯父世母。婿，已葬，婿之伯父致命女氏曰：『某之子有父母之喪，不得嗣為兄弟，使某致命。』女氏許諾，而弗敢嫁，禮也。婿，免喪，女之父母使人請，婿弗取，而後嫁之，禮也。女之父母死，婿亦如之。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 29", "sort_key": "0029", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「親迎，女在涂，而婿之父母死，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「親迎，女在涂，而婿之父母死，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 30", "sort_key": "0030", "text_original": "孔子曰：「女改服布深衣，縞總以趨喪。女在途，而女之父母死，則女反。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「女改服布深衣，縞總以趨喪。女在途，而女之父母死，則女反。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 31", "sort_key": "0031", "text_original": "「如婿親迎，女未至，而有齊衰大功之喪，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "「如婿親迎，女未至，而有齊衰大功之喪，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 32", "sort_key": "0032", "text_original": "孔子曰：「男不入，改服於外次；女入，改服於內次；然後即位而哭。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「男不入，改服於外次；女入，改服於內次；然後即位而哭。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 33, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 33", "sort_key": "0033", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「除喪則不復昏禮乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「除喪則不復昏禮乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 34, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 34", "sort_key": "0034", "text_original": "孔子曰：「祭，過時不祭，禮也；又何反於初？」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「祭，過時不祭，禮也；又何反於初？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 35, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 35", "sort_key": "0035", "text_original": "孔子曰：「嫁女之家，三夜不息燭，思相離也。取婦之家，三日不舉樂，思嗣親也。三月而廟見，稱來婦也。擇日而祭於禰，成婦之義也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「嫁女之家，三夜不息燭，思相離也。取婦之家，三日不舉樂，思嗣親也。三月而廟見，稱來婦也。擇日而祭於禰，成婦之義也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 36, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 36", "sort_key": "0036", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「女未廟見而死，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「女未廟見而死，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 37, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 37", "sort_key": "0037", "text_original": "孔子曰：「不遷於祖，不祔於皇姑，婿不杖、不菲、不次，歸葬于女氏之黨，示未成婦也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「不遷於祖，不祔於皇姑，婿不杖、不菲、不次，歸葬于女氏之黨，示未成婦也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 38, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 38", "sort_key": "0038", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「取女，有吉日而女死，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「取女，有吉日而女死，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 39, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 39", "sort_key": "0039", "text_original": "孔子曰：「婿齊衰而吊，既葬而除之。夫死亦如之。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「婿齊衰而吊，既葬而除之。夫死亦如之。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 40, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 40", "sort_key": "0040", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「喪有二孤，廟有二主，禮與？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「喪有二孤，廟有二主，禮與？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 41, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 41", "sort_key": "0041", "text_original": "孔子曰：「天無二日，土無二王，嘗禘郊社，尊無二上。未知其為禮也。昔者齊桓公亟舉兵，作偽主以行。及反，藏諸祖廟。廟有二主，自桓公始也。喪之二孤，則昔者衛靈公適魯，遭季桓子之喪，衛君請吊，哀公辭不得命，公為主，客人吊。康子立於門右，北面；公揖讓升自東階，西鄉；客升自西階吊。公拜，興，哭；康子拜稽顙於位，有司弗辯也。今之二孤，自季康子之過也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「天無二日，土無二王，嘗禘郊社，尊無二上。未知其為禮也。昔者齊桓公亟舉兵，作偽主以行。及反，藏諸祖廟。廟有二主，自桓公始也。喪之二孤，則昔者衛靈公適魯，遭季桓子之喪，衛君請吊，哀公辭不得命，公為主，客人吊。康子立於門右，北面；公揖讓升自東階，西鄉；客升自西階吊。公拜，興，哭；康子拜稽顙於位，有司弗辯也。今之二孤，自季康子之過也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 42, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 42", "sort_key": "0042", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，必以遷廟主行乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，必以遷廟主行乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 43, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 43", "sort_key": "0043", "text_original": "孔子曰：「天子巡守，以遷廟主行，載于齊車，言必有尊也。今也取七廟之主以行，則失之矣。當七廟、五廟無虛主；虛主者，唯天子崩，諸侯薨與去其國，與祫祭於祖，為無主耳。吾聞諸老聃曰：天子崩，國君薨，則祝取群廟之主而藏諸祖廟，禮也。卒哭成事而後，主各反其廟。君去其國，大宰取群廟之主以從，禮也。祫祭於祖，則祝迎四廟之主。主，出廟入廟必蹕；老聃云。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「天子巡守，以遷廟主行，載于齊車，言必有尊也。今也取七廟之主以行，則失之矣。當七廟、五廟無虛主；虛主者，唯天子崩，諸侯薨與去其國，與祫祭於祖，為無主耳。吾聞諸老聃曰：天子崩，國君薨，則祝取群廟之主而藏諸祖廟，禮也。卒哭成事而後，主各反其廟。君去其國，大宰取群廟之主以從，禮也。祫祭於祖，則祝迎四廟之主。主，出廟入廟必蹕；老聃云。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 44, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 44", "sort_key": "0044", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，無遷主，則何主？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「古者師行，無遷主，則何主？」", "notes": ""}
