{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 47, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 47", "sort_key": "0047", "text_original": "孔子曰：「天子、諸侯將出，必以幣帛皮圭告于祖禰，遂奉以出，載于齊車以行。每舍，奠焉而後就舍。反必告，設奠卒，斂幣玉，藏諸兩階之間，乃出。蓋貴命也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「天子、諸侯將出，必以幣帛皮圭告于祖禰，遂奉以出，載于齊車以行。每舍，奠焉而後就舍。反必告，設奠卒，斂幣玉，藏諸兩階之間，乃出。蓋貴命也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 48, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 48", "sort_key": "0048", "text_original": "子游問曰：「喪慈母如母，禮與？」", "text_normalized": "子游問曰：「喪慈母如母，禮與？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 49, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 49", "sort_key": "0049", "text_original": "孔子曰：「非禮也。古者，男子外有傅，內有慈母，君命所使教子也，何服之有？昔者，魯昭公少喪其母，有慈母良，及其死也，公弗忍也，欲喪之，有司以聞，曰：『古之禮，慈母無服，今也君為之服，是逆古之禮而亂國法也；若終行之，則有司將書之以遺後世。無乃不可乎！』公曰：『古者天子練冠以燕居。』公弗忍也，遂練冠以喪慈母。喪慈母，自魯昭公始也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「非禮也。古者，男子外有傅，內有慈母，君命所使教子也，何服之有？昔者，魯昭公少喪其母，有慈母良，及其死也，公弗忍也，欲喪之，有司以聞，曰：『古之禮，慈母無服，今也君為之服，是逆古之禮而亂國法也；若終行之，則有司將書之以遺後世。無乃不可乎！』公曰：『古者天子練冠以燕居。』公弗忍也，遂練冠以喪慈母。喪慈母，自魯昭公始也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 50, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 50", "sort_key": "0050", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「諸侯旅見天子，入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「諸侯旅見天子，入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 51, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 51", "sort_key": "0051", "text_original": "孔子曰：「四。」請問之。曰：「大廟火，日食，後之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。如諸侯皆在而日食，則從天子救日，各以其方色與其兵。大廟火，則從天子救火，不以方色與兵。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「四。」請問之。曰：「大廟火，日食，後之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。如諸侯皆在而日食，則從天子救日，各以其方色與其兵。大廟火，則從天子救火，不以方色與兵。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 52, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 52", "sort_key": "0052", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「諸侯相見，揖讓入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「諸侯相見，揖讓入門，不得終禮，廢者幾？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 53, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 53", "sort_key": "0053", "text_original": "孔子曰：「六。」請問之。曰：「天子崩，大廟火，日食，後夫人之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「六。」請問之。曰：「天子崩，大廟火，日食，後夫人之喪，雨沾服失容，則廢。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 54, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 54", "sort_key": "0054", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「天子嘗禘郊社五祀之祭，簠簋既陳，天子崩，後之喪，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「天子嘗禘郊社五祀之祭，簠簋既陳，天子崩，後之喪，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 55, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 55", "sort_key": "0055", "text_original": "孔子曰：「廢。」曾子問曰：「當祭而日食，太廟火，其祭也如之何？」孔子曰：「接祭而已矣。如牲至，未殺，則廢。天子崩，未殯，五祀之祭不行；既殯而祭，其祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣。自啟至于反哭，五祀之祭不行；已葬而祭，祝畢獻而已。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「廢。」曾子問曰：「當祭而日食，太廟火，其祭也如之何？」孔子曰：「接祭而已矣。如牲至，未殺，則廢。天子崩，未殯，五祀之祭不行；既殯而祭，其祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣。自啟至于反哭，五祀之祭不行；已葬而祭，祝畢獻而已。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 56, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 56", "sort_key": "0056", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「諸侯之祭社稷，俎豆既陳，聞天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪，如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「諸侯之祭社稷，俎豆既陳，聞天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪，如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 57, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 57", "sort_key": "0057", "text_original": "孔子曰：「廢。自薨比至於殯，自啟至于反哭，奉帥天子。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「廢。自薨比至於殯，自啟至于反哭，奉帥天子。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 58, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 58", "sort_key": "0058", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「大夫之祭，鼎俎既陳，籩豆既設，不得成禮，廢者幾？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「大夫之祭，鼎俎既陳，籩豆既設，不得成禮，廢者幾？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 59, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 59", "sort_key": "0059", "text_original": "孔子曰：「九。」請問之。曰：「天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪、君之大廟火、日食、三年之喪、齊衰、大功，皆廢。外喪自齊衰以下，行也。其齊衰之祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣；大功酢而已矣；小功、緦，室中之事而已矣。士之所以異者，緦不祭，所祭於死者無服則祭。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「九。」請問之。曰：「天子崩、後之喪、君薨、夫人之喪、君之大廟火、日食、三年之喪、齊衰、大功，皆廢。外喪自齊衰以下，行也。其齊衰之祭也，尸入，三飯不侑，酳不酢而已矣；大功酢而已矣；小功、緦，室中之事而已矣。士之所以異者，緦不祭，所祭於死者無服則祭。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 60, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 60", "sort_key": "0060", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「三年之喪，吊乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「三年之喪，吊乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 61, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 61", "sort_key": "0061", "text_original": "孔子曰：「三年之喪，練，不群立，不旅行。君子禮以飾情，三年之喪而吊哭，不亦虛乎？」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「三年之喪，練，不群立，不旅行。君子禮以飾情，三年之喪而吊哭，不亦虛乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 62, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 62", "sort_key": "0062", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「大夫、士有私喪，可以除之矣，而有君服焉，其除之也如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「大夫、士有私喪，可以除之矣，而有君服焉，其除之也如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 63, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 63", "sort_key": "0063", "text_original": "孔子曰：「有君喪服於身，不敢私服，又何除焉？於是乎有過時而弗除也。君之喪，服除而後殷祭，禮也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「有君喪服於身，不敢私服，又何除焉？於是乎有過時而弗除也。君之喪，服除而後殷祭，禮也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 64, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 64", "sort_key": "0064", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「父母之喪，弗除可乎？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「父母之喪，弗除可乎？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 65, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 65", "sort_key": "0065", "text_original": "孔子曰：「先王制禮，過時弗舉，禮也；非弗能勿除也，患其過於制也，故君子過時不祭，禮也。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「先王制禮，過時弗舉，禮也；非弗能勿除也，患其過於制也，故君子過時不祭，禮也。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 66, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 66", "sort_key": "0066", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「君薨，既殯，而臣有父母之喪，則如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「君薨，既殯，而臣有父母之喪，則如之何？」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 67, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 67", "sort_key": "0067", "text_original": "孔子曰：「歸居于家，有殷事，則之君所，朝夕否。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「歸居于家，有殷事，則之君所，朝夕否。」", "notes": ""}
