{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 69, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 69", "sort_key": "0069", "text_original": "孔子曰：「歸哭而反送君。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「歸哭而反送君。」", "notes": ""}
