{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 71, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 71", "sort_key": "0071", "text_original": "孔子曰：「歸殯，反于君所，有殷事則歸，朝夕否。大夫，室老行事；士，則子孫行事。大夫內子，有殷事，亦之君所，朝夕否。」", "text_normalized": "孔子曰：「歸殯，反于君所，有殷事則歸，朝夕否。大夫，室老行事；士，則子孫行事。大夫內子，有殷事，亦之君所，朝夕否。」", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 72, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 72", "sort_key": "0072", "text_original": "賤不誄貴，幼不誄長，禮也。唯天子，稱天以誄之。諸侯相誄，非禮也。", "text_normalized": "賤不誄貴，幼不誄長，禮也。唯天子，稱天以誄之。諸侯相誄，非禮也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "work_id": "liji", "section_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi", "source_id": "liji-007-the-questions-of-zeng-zi__cn-zh-1f6b1d3", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 73, "canonical_ref": "禮記·《曾子問》 73", "sort_key": "0073", "text_original": "曾子問曰：「君出疆以三年之戒，以椑從。君薨，其入如之何？」", "text_normalized": "曾子問曰：「君出疆以三年之戒，以椑從。君薨，其入如之何？」", "notes": ""}
